cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with object detection, which is a core problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves deep learning and kernel-based methods, which are both subfields of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also addresses the issue of training data imbalance, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed method on a real-world dataset, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
